FBIS4-42435 "drweu107_j_94003" FBIS-WEU-94-107 Daily Report 2 Jun 1994 ITALY & VATICAN CITY Bossi Too Busy for Dinner With Clinton Bossi Too Busy for Dinner With Clinton LD0206155894 Rome RAI Due Television Network in Italian 1430 GMT 2 Jun 94 LD0206155894 Rome RAI Due Television Network Italian BFN [Text] An RAI2 correspondent, introducing the news conference by U.S. President Clinton and Italian Prime Minister Berlusconi, said that Northern League Chairman Umberto Bossi may not attend the official dinner offered by Prime Minister Silvio Berlusconi tonight. The correspondent said Bossi said he could not attend because of prior engagements linked to the European election campaign.
